{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775872418491,"sessionID":"ses_285c1cf89ffectzDEDy3RAn9On","part":{"id":"prt_d7a3ea0880010KP2MXuvo6zs2m","messageID":"msg_d7a3e930e001Zyv4zDoLs04hDC","sessionID":"ses_285c1cf89ffectzDEDy3RAn9On","type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"toolu_6dc5f9670e574cc3801b4ec4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"mkdir -p changes/AR-031","description":"Create AR-031 directory"},"output":"","metadata":{"output":"","exit":0,"description":"Create AR-031 directory","truncated":false},"title":"Create AR-031 directory","time":{"start":1775872418474,"end":1775872418489}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775872418510,"sessionID":"ses_285c1cf89ffectzDEDy3RAn9On","part":{"id":"prt_d7a3ea2ba001AFCb37LSsJ4jK1","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d7a3e930e001Zyv4zDoLs04hDC","sessionID":"ses_285c1cf89ffectzDEDy3RAn9On","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":20128,"input":4018,"output":71,"reasoning":0,"cache":{"write":0,"read":16039}},"cost":0}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775872421629,"sessionID":"ses_285c1cf89ffectzDEDy3RAn9On","part":{"id":"prt_d7a3eaefc001F36MlpDTuOpi8U","messageID":"msg_d7a3ea2e3001a0OYoOKGNH4HDB","sessionID":"ses_285c1cf89ffectzDEDy3RAn9On","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775872439856,"sessionID":"ses_285c1cf89ffectzDEDy3RAn9On","part":{"id":"prt_d7a3eb072001grC3AZvOprqF9J","messageID":"msg_d7a3ea2e3001a0OYoOKGNH4HDB","sessionID":"ses_285c1cf89ffectzDEDy3RAn9On","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_815edd1c9a50450e8260281e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Delta Spec: AR-031 — RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding)\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing RBAC configuration (ServiceAccount, Role, RoleBinding) in the agentcube manifests module.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-031\n- **Module**: `manifests`\n- **Language**: YAML\n- **Size**: M\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: ServiceAccount Definitions\n\n### AR-031-001: Agent ServiceAccount\n\n- **GIVEN** Kubernetes namespace for agentcube components\n- **WHEN** creating ServiceAccount for agent pods\n- **THEN** it SHALL be named `agentcube-agent`\n- **AND** SHALL be created in each target namespace\n- **AND** SHALL include appropriate imagePullSecrets if needed\n\n### AR-031-002: Controller ServiceAccount\n\n- **GIVEN** namespace for agentcube control plane\n- **WHEN** creating ServiceAccount for controllers\n- **THEN** it SHALL be named `agentcube-controller`\n- **AND** SHALL be created in the agentcube-system namespace\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: Role Definitions\n\n### AR-031-003: Agent Runtime Role\n\n- **GIVEN** namespace for agent deployment\n- **WHEN** defining Role for agent ServiceAccount\n- **THEN** it SHALL include permissions for AgentRuntime CRD (get, list, watch)\n- **AND** SHALL include permissions for CodeInterpreter CRD (get, list, watch, update, patch)\n- **AND** SHALL include permissions forPods (get, list, watch, create, delete)\n- **AND** SHALL include permissions for Services (get, list, watch, create, update, delete)\n- **AND** SHALL be named `agentcube-agent-runtime`\n\n### AR-031-004: Agent Namespace Role\n\n- **GIVEN** namespace for agent deployment\n- **WHEN** defining Role for agent namespace access\n- **THEN** it SHALL include permissions for ConfigMaps (get, list, watch, create, update, delete)\n- **AND** SHALL include permissions for Secrets (get, list, watch, create, update, delete)\n- **AND** SHALL include permissions for Events (get, list, watch, create)\n- **AND** SHALL be named `agentcube-agent`\n\n### AR-031-005: Controller ClusterRole\n\n- **GIVEN** cluster-wide scope\n- **WHEN** defining ClusterRole for controller\n- **THEN** it SHALL include permissions for AgentRuntime CRD (all verbs)\n- **AND** SHALL include permissions for CodeInterpreter CRD (all verbs)\n- **AND** SHALL include permissions for namespaces (get, list, watch)\n- **AND** SHALL include permissions for pods (all verbs)\n- **AND** SHALL include permissions for services (all verbs)\n- **AND** SHALL include permissions for configmaps (all verbs)\n- **AND** SHALL include permissions for secrets (all verbs)\n- **AND** SHALL include permissions for events (all verbs)\n- **AND** SHALL be named `agentcube-controller`\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: RoleBinding Definitions\n\n### AR-031-006: Agent Runtime RoleBinding\n\n- **GIVEN** namespace for agent deployment\n- **WHEN** creating RoleBinding for agent ServiceAccount\n- **THEN** it SHALL bind `agentcube-agent` SA to `agentcube-agent-runtime` Role\n- **AND** SHALL be named `agentcube-agent-runtime`\n- **AND** SHALL reference correct namespace\n\n### AR-031-007: Agent Namespace RoleBinding\n\n- **GIVEN** namespace for agent deployment\n- **WHEN** creating RoleBinding for agent namespace access\n- **THEN** it SHALL bind `agentcube-agent` SA to `agentcube-agent` Role\n- **AND** SHALL be named `agentcube-agent`\n- **AND** SHALL reference correct namespace\n\n### AR-031-008: Controller RoleBinding\n\n- **GIVEN** agentcube-system namespace\n- **WHEN** creating RoleBinding for controller\n- **THEN** it SHALL bind `agentcube-controller` SA to `agentcube-controller` ClusterRole\n- **AND** SHALL be named `agentcube-controller`\n- **AND** SHALL use ClusterRoleBinding for cluster-wide access\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: RBAC Deployment\n\n### AR-031-009: RBAC YAML structure\n\n- **GIVEN** manifests directory\n- **WHEN** organizing RBAC YAML files\n- **THEN** they SHALL be placed under `manifests/rbac/`\n- **AND** SHALL include ServiceAccount YAML files\n- **AND** SHALL include Role YAML files\n- **AND** SHALL include RoleBinding YAML files\n\n### AR-031-010: Namespace isolation\n\n- **GIVEN** RBAC configuration\n- **WHEN** defining roles\n- **THEN** Agent roles SHALL be namespace-scoped (Role)\n- **AND** Controller roles SHALL be cluster-scoped (ClusterRole)\n- **AND** RoleBindings SHALL reference correct namespaces\n\n### AR-031-011: Least privilege principle\n\n- **GIVEN** RBAC configuration\n- **WHEN** defining permissions\n- **THEN** Agent SA SHALL only have permissions needed for runtime\n- **AND** Controller SA SHALL have permissions needed for reconciliation\n- **AND** No wildcard (*) permissions SHALL be used unless absolutely necessary\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: Validation\n\n### AR-031-012: YAML syntax validation\n\n- **GIVEN** RBAC YAML files\n- **WHEN** running `kubectl apply --dry-run=client`\n- **THEN** all YAMLs SHALL be valid Kubernetes resources\n- **AND** SHALL pass schema validation\n\n### AR-031-013: RBAC consistency\n\n- **GIVEN** RBAC configuration\n- **WHEN** applying to cluster\n- **THEN** ServiceAccounts SHALL exist before RoleBindings reference them\n- **AND** Roles SHALL exist before RoleBindings reference them\n- **AND** All referenced namespaces SHALL exist\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Kubernetes RBAC Documentation\n- agentcube design: `design.md`","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-031/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-031/delta-spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-031/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775872439844,"end":1775872439853}}}}
